int sumEven(int arr[], int n) {
    int sum = 0;
    for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
        if (arr[i] % 2 == 0)
            sum += arr[i];
    }
    return sum;
}
```
Simple iteration checking each element with modulus operator. arr[i] % 2 == 0 checks if even. Time: O(n), Space: O(1).

